|title=Sunmi Earns Best U.S. Sales Week Yet With 'Heroine' Single|last=Benjamin|first=Jeff|website=Billboard|publisher=Eldridge Industries|accessdate=February 6, 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180208174851/https://www.billboard.com/articles/columns/k-town/8097742/sunmi-heroine-best-us-sales-week-charts|archivedate=February 8, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Siren (Sunmi song)|Siren]]\" {{small|({{lang|ko|\uc0ac\uc774\ub80c}})}}\n| 1 || 1 || 5\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{n/a}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Noir (song)|Noir]]\" {{small|({{lang|ko|\ub204\uc544\ub974}})}}\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2019\n| 8 || 9 || 3\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{N/A|Non-album singles}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Lalalay]]\" {{small|({{lang|ko|\ub0a0\ub77c\ub9ac}})}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.instagram.com/p/B1Qkn7vD_1A/|title=LALALAY is coming \ud83e\udd1f\ud83c\udffc\u2764\ufe0f \ub0a0\ub77c\ub9ac \ub0a0\ub77c\ub9ac \ub0a0\ub77c\ub9ac|via=[[Instagram]]|date=August 17, 2019|accessdate=August 18, 2019}}</ref>\n| 8 || 1 || 4\n|\n* US: 1,000<ref name=\"lalalay\">{{cite web|url=https://www.billboard.com/articles/business/chart-beat/8529350/sunmi-lalalay-fifth-top-5-hit-world-digital-song-sales-chart|title=Sunmi Earns Fifth Top 5 Hit on World Digital Song Sales Chart With 'Lalalay'|last=Benjamin|first=Jeff|website=Billboard|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=September 23, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! colspan=\"8\" | Collaborations\n|-\n! scope=row | \"You\" {{small|([[B1A4]] feat. Sunmi)}}\n|2014\n| 63 || 91 || \u2014\n| {{NA}}\n|''[[Solo Day]]''\n|-\n! colspan=\"8\" | Soundtrack appearances\n|-\n! scope=row | \"Gotta Go\" {{small|({{lang|ko|\uac00\ub77c\uace0 }})}}\n|2020\n| 123 || \u2014 || \u2014\n| {{NA}}\n|''[[XX (web series)|XX OST Part 1]]''\n|-\n! colspan=\"8\" | Other charted songs\n|-\n! scope=row | \"Burn\"\n| rowspan=\"4\"|2014\n| 159 || rowspan=\"4\" {{NA}} || \u2014\n| rowspan=\"4\" {{NA}}\n| rowspan=\"4\"|''Full Moon''\n|-\n! scope=row | \"Who Am I\" {{small|(feat. [[Kim Yu-bin (musician)|Yubin