een Elizabeth Theatre\n|-\n|March 18, 2019\n|United States\n|Washington D.C\n|Lincoln Theatre\n|-\n|March 21, 2019\n|Mexico\n|Mexico City\n|Auditorio Blackberry\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" |Asia\n|-\n|April 13, 2019\n| colspan=\"2\" |Hong Kong\n|KITEC Star Hall\n|-\n|May 10, 2019\n|Taiwan\n|Taipei\n|Taiwan University Sports Centre\n|-\n|May 23, 2019\n|Japan\n|Tokyo\n|TSUTAYA O-East\n|-\n! colspan=\"4\" |Europe\n|-\n|May 30, 2019\n|United Kingdom\n|London\n|Indigo at The O2\n|-\n|June 2, 2019\n|Poland\n|Warsaw\n|Progresja\n|-\n|June 4, 2019\n|Netherlands\n|Amsterdam\n|Q-Factory\n|-\n|June 6, 2019\n|Germany\n|Berlin\n|Huxley's Neue Welt\n|-\n|June 7, 2019\n|France\n|Paris\n|La Cigale\n|}\n\n==Awards and nominations==\n{{See also|List of awards and nominations received by Wonder Girls}}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n! Year\n! Award\n! Category\n! Nominated work\n! Result\n!Ref.\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|2013\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[2013 Mnet Asian Music Awards|15th Mnet Asian Music Awards]]\n| [[Mnet Asian Music Award for Best Female Artist|Best Female Artist]]\n| {{NA}}\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| [[Mnet Asian Music Award for Best Dance Performance|Best Dance Performance \u2013 Female Solo]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|\"24 Hours\"\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\"|2014\n| rowspan=\"2\"|23rd [[Seoul Music Awards]]\n| Bonsang Award\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| Popularity Award\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{NA}}\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[2014 Mnet Asian Music Awards|16th Mnet Asian Music Awards]]\n| Best Female Artist\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| Best Dance Performance \u2013 Solo\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\"Full Moon\"\n| {{won}}\n|<ref name=\"Winners\">{{cite web|url=http://mama.interest.me/2014mama/winners|title=Mnet Asian Music Awards 2014 Winners|website=Mnet Asian Music Awards|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150504102323/http://mama.interest.me/2014mama/winners|archive-date=May 4, 2015|url-status=dead|access-date=January 28, 2014}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.m