bsite=Billboard}}</ref>\n|-\n| Best Dance Performance \u2013 Solo\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|\"[[Gashina]]\"\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| 9th [[Melon Music Awards]]\n| Best Dance \u2013 Female\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"22\"|2018\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[32nd Golden Disc Awards]]\n| Digital Bonsang\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| Global Popularity Award\n| {{NA}}\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|27th [[Seoul Music Awards]]\n| Bonsang Award\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\"[[Gashina]]\"\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| Popularity Award\n| rowspan=\"2\" {{NA}}\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| Hallyu Special Award\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| 7th [[Gaon Chart Music Awards]]\n| Song of the Year \u2013 August\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|\"[[Gashina]]\"\n| {{won}}\n|<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://entertain.naver.com/now/read?oid=421&aid=0003209519|title=[\uac00\uc628\ucc28\ud2b8\uc5b4\uc6cc\ub4dc] \uc544\uc774\uc720 5\uad00\uc655 \ub4f1\uadf9+\uc6cc\ub108\uc6d0 \ub3cc\ud48d \uac70\uc14c\ub2e4(\uc885\ud569)|date=February 14, 2018|website=Naver|publisher=News1|language=ko}}</ref>\n|-\n| 15th [[Korean Music Awards]]\n| Best Pop Song\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"|1st [[MBC Plus X Genie Music Awards]]\n| Artist of the Year\n| rowspan=\"9\" {{NA}}\n| {{nom}}\n| rowspan=\"3\" |<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.soompi.com/article/1238753wpp/2018-mbc-plus-x-genie-music-awards-announces-nominees-voting-begins|title=2018 MBC Plus X Genie Music Awards Announces Nominees + Voting Begins|date=October 1, 2018|website=Soompi}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://entertain.naver.com/read?oid=076&aid=0003322539|title=\"BTS\u00b7\uc6cc\ub108\uc6d0\u00b7\ud2b8\uc640\uc774\uc2a4\u00b7\ubcfc\ube68\uac04\"\u2026'2018 MGA' \ud6c4\ubcf4 \uacf5\uac1c, \ud22c\ud45c \uc2dc\uc791|date=October 1, 2018|website=Naver}}</ref>\n|-\n| Female Artist Award\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| Genie Music Popularity Award\n| {{nom}}\n|-\n| 2nd Elle Style Awards\n| Best Music Icon\n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|3rd [[Asia Artist Awards]]\n| Artist of the Year, Singer\n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| Best Music Award\n| {{won}}\n|\n|-\n| 10th [[Melon Music Awards]]\n| Top 10 Artists\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| 2nd [[Soribada Best K-Music Awards]]\n| Bonsang Award\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=EXO, BTS and more nominated for a Bonsang at the Soribada Music Awards |url=https://www.sbs.com.au/popasia/blog/2018/06/21/exo-bts-and-more-nominated-bonsang-soribada-music-awards |website=SBS PopAsia |accessdate=August 23, 2019 |language=en |date=June 21, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[2018 Mnet Asian Music Awards|20th Mnet Asian Music Awards]]\n| [[Mnet Asian Music Award for Best Female Artist|Best Female Artist]]\n| {{won}}\n| <ref>{{cite web |title=2018 MAMA Winners |url=https://www.mwave.me/en/mama/history/winners/list?years=2018 |website=Mwave |accessdate=March 13, 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Mnet Asian Music Award for Best Dance Performance|Best Dance Performance \u2013 Female Solo]]\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\"[[Warning (Sunmi EP)|Siren]]\"\n| {{nom}}\n| <ref>{{cite news |last1=Johnson |first1=Nia |title=Here Are All Of The 2018 MAMA Nominations + Current Leaders |url=https://www.mwave.me/en/mama/history/news/view/NEWS2018116659/here-are-all-of-the-2018-mama-nominations-current-leaders?_position=144&_cnMtCtgyId=1064&years=2018 |accessdate=March 13, 2019 |work=Mwave |date=November 2, 2018}}</ref>\n|-\n| Korea First Brand Awards\n| Most Anticipated Female Solo Singer\n| rowspan=\"3\" {{NA}}\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\"|1st Korea Popular Music Awards\n| Best Artist\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| Popularity Award\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| Best Digital Song\n| rowspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;\"|\"[[Warning (Sunmi EP)|Siren]]\"\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| Best Solo Dance Track\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"12\"|2019\n| rowspan=\"2\"|[[33rd Golden Disc Awards]]\n| Digital Daesang\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"|\"[[Heroine (Sunmi song)|Heroine]]\"\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| Popularity Award\n| {{NA}}\n| {{nom}}\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\"